00:13:35.020 --> 00:13:36.910 align:middle line:90%
because I know a lot about that.

00:13:36.910 --> 00:13:42.970 align:middle line:84%
So yes, from age 4 to 13, I
was molested by my father.

00:13:42.970 --> 00:13:45.010 align:middle line:90%
And I kept silent about it.

00:13:45.010 --> 00:13:47.230 align:middle line:84%
There were wonderful
people and different times

00:13:47.230 --> 00:13:49.000 align:middle line:84%
that I could have
said something.

00:13:49.000 --> 00:13:50.560 align:middle line:90%
And I stayed silent.

00:13:50.560 --> 00:13:52.390 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Why?

00:13:52.390 --> 00:13:54.970 align:middle line:90%
>>SANCHEZ: For fear--

00:13:54.970 --> 00:13:56.160 align:middle line:90%
