mom were so important to me.

00:14:01.300 --> 00:14:04.580 align:middle line:84%
And I didn't know
what would happen.

00:14:04.580 --> 00:14:06.940 align:middle line:84%
He did say that,
if I kept quiet,

00:14:06.940 --> 00:14:08.980 align:middle line:84%
he wouldn't bother
my younger sister.

00:14:08.980 --> 00:14:10.840 align:middle line:84%
But that was a lie,
because later--

00:14:10.840 --> 00:14:14.410 align:middle line:90%
later-- so there was that.

00:14:14.410 --> 00:14:16.570 align:middle line:84%
There was shame--
a lot of shame,

00:14:16.570 --> 00:14:20.940 align:middle line:84%
like, that other people probably
weren't experiencing anything

00:14:20.940 --> 00:14:21.740 align:middle line:90%
like this.

00:14:21.740 --> 00:14:23.137 align:middle line:90%
And so it was like, oh my gosh.

00:14:23.137 --> 00:14:24.220 align:middle line:90%
I had to keep this secret.

00:14:24.220 --> 00:14:25.660 align:middle line:90%
And it only really end--

00:14:25.660 --> 00:14:28.780 align:middle line:84%
I can't even own that
it was me, growing

00:14:28.780 --> 00:14:30.550 align:middle line:84%
and becoming more
mature and understanding

00:14:30.550 --> 00:14:32.710 align:middle line:90%
that this was about my freedom.

00:14:32.710 --> 00:14:36.700 align:middle line:84%
But my father was
murdered when I was 13.

00:14:36.700 --> 00:14:39.640 align:middle line:84%
And he was mistaken--
it was racial.

00:14:39.640 --> 00:14:41.947 align:middle line:84%
So it kind of fits
with what's continuing

00:14:41.947 --> 00:14:43.030 align:middle line:90%
to happen in this country.

00:14:43.030 --> 00:14:45.160 align:middle line:84%
But he went for a
beer after work.

00:14:45.160 --> 00:14:48.730 align:middle line:84%
And early that day, a white man
and a black man, in the '60s,

00:14:48.730 --> 00:14:50.260 align:middle line:90%
were having an argument.

00:14:50.260 --> 00:14:52.907 align:middle line:84%
The white man returned and
saw my father sitting there

00:14:52.907 --> 00:14:54.490 align:middle line:84%
and fired two bullets
through his head

00:14:54.490 --> 00:14:55.960 align:middle line:84%
and killed him on
the spot, thinking--

00:14:55.960 --> 00:14:56.920 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Thinking it
was the other man.

00:14:56.920 --> 00:14:58.628 align:middle line:84%
>>SANCHEZ: Thinking
it was the other man.

00:14:58.628 --> 00:15:00.070 align:middle line:90%
And you can imagine--

00:15:00.070 --> 00:15:04.060 align:middle line:84%
a 13-year-old-- I was dealing
