00:15:09.640 --> 00:15:10.720 align:middle line:90%
the unthinkable.

00:15:10.720 --> 00:15:15.680 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: When you heard that
news, what did you feel?

00:15:15.680 --> 00:15:18.190 align:middle line:84%
>>SANCHEZ: Well, when the
police came to the door,

00:15:18.190 --> 00:15:19.690 align:middle line:90%
I was with my mom.

00:15:19.690 --> 00:15:22.600 align:middle line:90%
And they invited themselves in.

00:15:22.600 --> 00:15:27.370 align:middle line:84%
And I remember them
saying, Mrs. Sanchez, there

00:15:27.370 --> 00:15:29.140 align:middle line:90%
was an accident that happened.

00:15:29.140 --> 00:15:32.830 align:middle line:84%
And do you know anyone who
would want to harm your husband?

00:15:32.830 --> 00:15:37.990 align:middle line:84%
And I remember, in my
head, thinking, oh my gosh.

00:15:37.990 --> 00:15:40.940 align:middle line:90%
I wanted-- I wanted him gone.

00:15:40.940 --> 00:15:44.510 align:middle line:84%
And then they told
what had happened,

00:15:44.510 --> 00:15:48.680 align:middle line:84%
how he had been killed and
the circumstances of it.

00:15:48.680 --> 00:15:51.790 align:middle line:84%
And I remember, at that point,
just all these different

00:15:51.790 --> 00:15:54.820 align:middle line:84%
things-- confusion, I think,
is the biggest thing--

00:15:54.820 --> 00:16:00.250 align:middle line:84%
fear, sadness, confusion,
wanting to support my mom.

00:16:00.250 --> 00:16:02.740 align:middle line:84%
And it wasn't until years
later that I realized,

00:16:02.740 --> 00:16:06.840 align:middle line:84%
when I did talk to my mom,
when I confronted her,

00:16:06.840 --> 00:16:13.870 align:middle line:84%
at 21, that we both realized
that we were experiencing

00:16:13.870 --> 00:16:16.460 align:middle line:84%
some of the same
things in that moment.

00:16:16.460 --> 00:16:20.080 align:middle line:84%
Because she didn't know, but
she had a sense something

00:16:20.080 --> 00:16:23.020 align:middle line:90%
was not right with him.

00:16:23.020 --> 00:16:25.091 align:middle line:90%
And it makes sense, so it was--

00:16:25.091 --> 00:16:26.090 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: At that moment--

00:16:26.090 --> 00:16:27.160 align:middle line:90%
>>SANCHEZ: --a hard thing.

00:16:27.160 --> 00:16:28.285 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: --your father left.

00:16:28.285 --> 00:16:29.260 align:middle line:90%
Your violator left.

00:16:29.260 --> 00:16:30.310 align:middle line:90%
>>SANCHEZ: Yes-- yes.

00:16:30.310 --> 00:16:35.680 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So did you start to
feel, in any way, a little bit

00:16:35.680 --> 00:16:36.640 align:middle line:90%
more freedom?

00:16:36.640 --> 00:16:37.840 align:middle line:90%
Or did you hold onto that--

00:16:37.840 --> 00:16:38.230 align:middle line:90%
>>SANCHEZ: Well, no-- no.

00:16:38.230 --> 00:16:39.050 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: --for a long time?

00:16:39.050 --> 00:16:41.383 align:middle line:84%
>>SANCHEZ: And so this is an
important part of the story

00:16:41.383 --> 00:16:43.640 align:middle line:84%
too that lots of people
don't get to hear.

00:16:43.640 --> 00:16:48.040 align:middle line:90%
But I thought, it would be--

00:16:48.040 --> 00:16:50.050 align:middle line:90%
I would now be able to be free.

00:16:50.050 --> 00:16:51.070 align:middle line:90%
This is what I wanted.

00:16:51.070 --> 00:16:54.400 align:middle line:84%
But the mind-- so all the
images and things continued.

00:16:54.400 --> 00:16:58.150 align:middle line:84%
So I did do what, unfortunately,
is still on the rise

00:16:58.150 --> 00:17:01.030 align:middle line:84%
everywhere in the world,
