00:17:11.290 --> 00:17:12.490 align:middle line:90%
the images aren't gone.

00:17:12.490 --> 00:17:15.410 align:middle line:84%
And I still hadn't
told anybody about it.

00:17:15.410 --> 00:17:16.990 align:middle line:90%
And luckily-- fortunately--

00:17:16.990 --> 00:17:19.130 align:middle line:84%
I feel like-- oh,
Spirit was with me--

00:17:19.130 --> 00:17:21.430 align:middle line:90%
I took aspirins-- a lot of them.

00:17:21.430 --> 00:17:23.712 align:middle line:90%
And it didn't work.

00:17:23.712 --> 00:17:24.920 align:middle line:90%
It's kind of absurd in a way.

00:17:24.920 --> 00:17:26.560 align:middle line:84%
I remember just
