together and enjoy life

00:56:59.040 --> 00:57:03.120 align:middle line:10%
for the three days, be
joyful, identify the problems

00:57:03.120 --> 00:57:04.890 align:middle line:10%
and solutions that are working.

00:57:04.890 --> 00:57:06.169 align:middle line:90%
It's very solutions oriented--

00:57:06.169 --> 00:57:07.210 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That are working.

00:57:07.210 --> 00:57:10.500 align:middle line:84%
>>SANCHEZ: And
really lift those up.

00:57:10.500 --> 00:57:12.390 align:middle line:84%
I almost feel the
vibration of that.

00:57:12.390 --> 00:57:14.940 align:middle line:84%
As we do that, we
make those changes.

00:57:14.940 --> 00:57:16.500 align:middle line:90%
And it's really wonderful.

00:57:16.500 --> 00:57:19.120 align:middle line:10%
And it's seeing what's really
happening all over the world--

00:57:19.120 --> 00:57:22.260 align:middle line:10%
the things we don't get to
hear about that are working--

00:57:22.260 --> 00:57:25.140 align:middle line:10%
that we need to send
more light, love,

00:57:25.140 --> 00:57:29.470 align:middle line:10%
resources to, to make this
world be what it's meant to be,

00:57:29.470 --> 00:57:30.700 align:middle line:10%
which is thriving.

00:57:30.700 --> 00:57:33.284 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That's so important-- a
solution-oriented conference--

00:57:33.284 --> 00:57:34.083 align:middle line:90%
>>SANCHEZ: Yes.

00:57:34.083 --> 00:57:36.540 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: --with all of the
leaders of the world and more.

00:57:36.540 --> 00:57:39.952 align:middle line:84%
And it's also
broadcast worldwide--

00:57:39.952 --> 00:57:41.160 align:middle line:90%
>>SANCHEZ: It is going to be.

